<h2>Welcome to Earthkin Nature School!</h2>

<p>Dear <%= @parent.full_name %>,</p>

<p>Thank you for your enrollment application! We're excited to have you join the Earthkin community.</p>

<p>We've created an account for you so you can track your application progress and manage your enrollment online.</p>

<h3>Your Login Credentials</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @parent.email %></li>
  <li><strong>Temporary Password:</strong> <code><%= @temporary_password %></code></li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Please change your password after your first login for security.</strong></p>

<p><a href="<%= @login_url %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #2E7D32; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; margin: 16px 0;">Log In to Your Account</a></p>

<h3>What's Next?</h3>
<p>Once you log in, you'll be able to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>View your application status</li>
  <li>Complete any pending forms</li>
  <li>Track payment installments</li>
  <li>View your child's class schedule</li>
  <li>Communicate with teachers and staff</li>
</ul>

<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out.</p>

<p>Warmly,<br>
The Earthkin Team</p>
